      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black over Cinnamon Nappa leather. This example is powered by the high-revving S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing, all operating within factory-spec tolerances. The 6-speed Getrag 420G manual gearbox provides crisp engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. Critically, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed\u2014eliminating the two primary mechanical concerns for this chassis. The suspension retains its original kinematics with fresh OEM bushings and Sachs dampers. Paint meter readings confirm original finish across all panels, and the undercarriage is free of any electrolytic corrosion. A mechanically transparent, turn-key masterpiece for the serious collector.",
